column1: {{discussion top|The fate of this property has not been determined. Feel free to start another dicussion or request later. [[User:Matěj Suchánek|Matěj Suchánek]] ([[User talk:Matěj Suchánek|{{int:Talkpagelinktext}}]]) 14:20, 9 July 2017 (UTC)

}} Meanwhile, we have got a new property {{P|2439}}. Its usage is marginal compared to these two properties, that's why I haven't mentioned it in the conclusion. But I think we have a good opportunity to make another decision about this one. : {{ping|Matěj Suchánek}} Do we reaaly need a discussion about the fate of {{P|2439}} ? This is clear that this property should be merged with the future unique property. [[User:Snipre|Snipre]] ([[User talk:Snipre|{{int:Talkpagelinktext}}]]) 20:19, 28 May 2017 (UTC)
